                        </p>
                        <p style="padding-left: 40px;">
                            14.9&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Governing Law; Submission to Jurisdiction</span>. The Agreement is governed by and construed in accordance with the internal laws of the State of
                            Delaware without giving effect to any choice or conflict of law provision.
                        </p>
                        <p style="padding-left: 40px;">
                            14.10&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Waiver of Jury Trial</span>. Each party irrevocably and unconditionally waives any right it may have to a trial by jury in respect of any legal
