                        <p style="padding-left: 40px;">
                            14.13&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Not Construed Against Drafter</span>. The language of the Agreement shall not be interpreted in favor of or against any Party as the drafter of the
                            Agreement.
